2. 根據12指引睇吓邊個組織係共諜，都係有冇收外國錢、有冇同共產黨同一口徑咁<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tup9aQy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ftup9aQy.png&h=e3450ba2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gqoNGXe.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgqoNGXe.png&h=554eacd6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n3. 叫人督灰俾FBI<br />\n<br />\n強調意見唔同不等於共諜<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RiLDOCF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRiLDOCF.png&h=53845bd9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jJzdCwa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjJzdCwa.png&h=2265204c&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T12:31:30.000Z","msg":"應該學以前咁<br />\n<br />\n全面清算共產或左翼思想<br />\n<br />\n可惜而家荷李活左到仆街"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T18:03:15.000Z","msg":"荷李活都叫左應該激到啲共產黨員番生<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e654bd242c4555373b74dbf49ff639a37c9d1605","tid":2220161,"uid":270889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T18:06:25.000Z","msg":"諗起套戲<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=XULIO67YIRA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DXULIO67YIRA&d=4SaXJ4tauImRU00LhBBHUgPtErjweJPees2C482IDEo%3D&h=50555419\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=XULIO67YIRA</a><br />\n<br />\nAs the face of law enforcement in America for almost 50 years, J. Edgar Hoover was feared and admired, reviled and revered. But behind closed doors, he held secrets that would have destroyed his image, his career and his life."},{"pid":"635e89ddfecd323b6dce6103e17cfd5affdd2684","tid":2220161,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2bd7e0e68896f171a715201b7d61610640b09012","tid":2220161,"uid":48083,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T12:54:25.000Z"